<knimeNode icon="./centroids.png" type="Manipulator" xmlns="http://knime.org/node/v2.8" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:schemaLocation="http://knime.org/node/v2.10 http://knime.org/node/v2.10.xsd">
    <name>Centroids</name>
    
    <shortDescription>
        Find centroid of a geometry
    </shortDescription>
    
    <fullDescription>
        <intro>
        This node returns the <a href="http://javadox.com/com.vividsolutions/jts/1.13/com/vividsolutions/jts/geom/Geometry.html#getCentroid()">centroids of geometries</a> 
        listed in input table and replace the geometry column with list of Points. The input table must contain a geometry column with the name "the_geom"" and geometries must be in GeoJSON format.
		</intro>
        
        
